          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When there is moral rot within a nation, its government topples easily. But wise and knowledgeable leaders bring stability. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When there is moral rot within a nation, its government topples easily. But wise and knowledgeable leaders bring stability."
